Are so.. Grr.

Thats ALL highschool is.. Drama. 

Ooh well, I guess we all have to live with it. But seriously, some girls need to step back and see how they act in some SIMPLE situations. It's crazy.. 

But anyways, me and Liz went bowling this weekend and totally got hit on by some hot St Martin fellers **fellers=AMANDA's word** not mine! We're getting some people to go to the movies this Friday, so if your up for it just tell me! 

Proms coming up sorta soon! I dont have a date.. really want to go with someone! I mean, going with friends would def. be awesome, but I dont know.. I just want to have a date this year... so I'm just crossing my fingers!
